It's basically impossible to explain to zoomers that a decade ago the internet was totally infested by a group of men called "bronies" who were obsessed with a children's TV show about cartoon unicorns and used to spam porn of the characters all over various websites all the time

You couldn't go on 4chan or play a game of TF2 without seeing someone's spray of cartoon ponies having graphic horse sex, everyone on forums had brony avatars, there was no escaping from it and it was hell on earth, then disappeared overnight and we collectively blanked it out.
There's probably a "default state" in the USA but I am unsure which one
